quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  5,109,"√Ďaande Alla Moo…ďoyta Nulaa…ďe …ďen, O Daala: "Ko hol…óum njaabano…óon?" …ďe maaka: "ganndal alanaa amen, pellet, An, ko An woni ganndu…óo ko wirnii"."
  5,110,"Tuma nde Alla Daalunoo : "Ko an yo Iisaa …ďi…ó…óo Maryama, siftor dokkam …óe e dow maa…óa e dow yumma maa…óa, tuma nde Mi Semmbinirno maa fittaandu laa…ďunde ndun, ha…óa yeewta yim…ďe …ďen ka penuyaagal e ka ∆īa∆ī∆īurmayaagal. E tuma nde mi Anndinno maa binndugol ngol e √Īe√Ī∆īangal ngal, e Tawreeta e Linjiila. E tuma tagayno…óaa e loope wano mbaadi sonndu e DuŇčayee An ; nguttaa e mayru ndu laatoo sonndu e DuŇčayee Am Sellinaa bun…óo e …óamaa…óo e DuŇčayee Am. E tuma nde yaltinanyno…óaa maay…ďe e DuŇčayee Am. E tuma nde Mi Surnoo …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen e maa…óa nde ngddanno…óaa …ďe …ďanngannduyeeji (pee√Ī…ói)…ói,yeddu…ďe …ďe e ma…ď…ďe mbi'i: "…óum wonaali si wanaa mbilewu pee√Īungu"."
  5,111,"Tuma nde mbahyiimi e laa…ďam…ďe ma …ďen, si ko woni: "ngooŇč…óinee kam in e Nulaa…óo Am o", …ďe mbi'i: "min gooŇč…óinii, seedito won de pellet, ko min jebbilii…ďe"."
  5,112,"Tuma nde laa…ďam…ďe [ma] …ďen mbinoo: "Ko an yo Iisaa, …ďi…ó…óo Maryama, hara Joomi maa hino waawi nde O jippinanta men kooliwal immorde ka kammu?" O maaki: "kulee Alla, si on laatike gooŇč…óin…ďe"."
  5,113,"∆Āe mb'i: "minn faala √Īaamde e maggal, …ďer…óe amen …óen dee∆īa, min gannda gooŇč…óii a goonganii amen, mn ngona e maggal jeyaa…ďe e seeditii…ďe"."